==English==
===Adjective===
'''collectible'''
# worthy or suitable to be [[collected]] on historical/financial grounds, or for meeting a personal aesthetic: ''collectible stamps'', ''collectible china'', ''collectible Beatles memorabilia'' 
# rightfully subject to payment: ''a collectible bill'' 
===Noun===
'''collectible'''
# object which someone might want to [[collect]]
===Alternative spellings===
*[[collectable]] (substandard)